}}</ref>。Cliver和Svalgaard<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.leif.org/research/1859%20Storm%20-%20Extreme%20Space%20Weather.pdf
|last1=Cliver
|last2=Svalgaard
|title=The 1859 solar–terrestrial disturbance and the current limits of extreme space weather activity
|date=2004
