1212-X1.4flare.html|title=Big Sunspot 1520 Releases X1.4 Class Flare With Earth-Directed CME|date=July 12, 2012|publisher=''NASA''|accessdate=July 14, 2012|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214134253/https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/sunearth/news/News071212-X1.4flare.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在這個星期內，於2012年7月15日侵襲地球<ref>{{cite news | url= http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-14/science/32674301_1_solar-storm-space-weather-prediction-center-sun-storms | title= Solar storm rising, to hit Earth today | publisher= ''The Times of India'' | accessdate= July 14, 2012 | archive-date= 2013-11-11 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131111223149/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-14/science/32674301_1_solar-storm-space-weather-prediction-center-sun-storms | dead-url= yes }}</ref>，還有G1-G2的[[磁暴|地磁風暴]]事件<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2012/07/201271573711607.html | title='Minor' solar storm reaches Earth | publisher=''aljazeera.com'' | accessdate=July 15, 2012 | archive-date=2020-04-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427151449/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2012/07/201271573711607.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://img404.imageshack.us/img404/3067/alertstimeline17573.png | title=Space Weather Alerts and Warnings Timeline: July 16, 2012 | publisher=''[[National_Oceanic_and_Atmospheric_Administration|NOAA]]'' | accessdate=July 17, 2012 | archive-date=2013-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111224553/http://img404.imageshack.us/img404/3067/alertstimeline17573.png | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年10月24日出現X1.8級的閃焰<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1002029/sun-unleashes-powerful-solar-flare|title=Sun Unleashes Powerful Solar Flare|date=October 24, 2012|publisher=''Sky News''|accessdate=October 24, 2012|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003212901/http://news.sky.com/story/1002029/sun-unleashes-powerful-solar-flare|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年初，已經有巨大的太陽閃焰活動，特別是在2013年5月12日開始的48小時內，共有4個X級的太陽閃焰，強度從X1.2以上至X3.2<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/sun-solar-flare-space-318/ |title=rt.com |access-date=2015-05-13 |archive-date=2021-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428202356/https://www.rt.com/news/sun-solar-flare-space-318/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；後者是2013年最強大的閃焰之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/sunearth/news/News051213-flare.html |title=Three X-class Flares in 24 Hours |access-date=2015-05-13 |archive-date=2021-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430165249/https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/sunearth/news/News051213-flare.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Malik, Tariq. "Major Solar Flare Erupts from the Sun, Strongest of 2013". Space.com managing editor, 13 May 2013.</ref>。離開複雜的太陽黑子活動區AR2035-AR2046，在2014年4月25日0032UT爆發了強烈的X1.3級太陽閃焰，並且中斷了地球白晝區域的短波通訊。NASA的太陽動力學天文台記錄到[http://sdowww.lmsal.com/sdomedia/SunInTime/2014/04/25/f_211_193_171.jpg 這個閃焰] {{Wayback|url=http://sdowww.lmsal.com/sdomedia/SunInTime/2014/04/25/f_211_193_171.jpg |date=20160604115539 }}和來自這次爆炸的極紫外線輻射。

== 閃焰噴射 ==
閃焰噴射是和太陽閃焰相關聯的一種噴發類型<ref name="Moromoto">{{cite web|url=http://wwwsoc.nii.ac.jp/jepsjmo/cd-rom/2002cd-rom/pdf/e021/e021-005_e.pdf|title=Effects of Magnetic and Gravity forces on the Acceleration of Solar Filaments and Coronal Mass Ejections|author=Tarou Morimoto|author2=Hiroki Kurokawa|accessdate=2009-10-08|format=pdf|archive-date=2011-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611232648/http://wwwsoc.nii.ac.jp/jepsjmo/cd-rom/2002cd-rom/pdf/e021/e021-005_e.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。它們涉及比日珥噴發更快速噴出的物質<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/kg6u717443825g41/|title=Dynamics of flare sprays|author=E. Tandberg-Hanssen|author2=Sara F. Martin|author3=Richard T. Hansen|last-author-amp=yes|publisher=Solar Physics|date=1980}}{{Dead link|date=2020年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，並達到每秒20至200公里的速度<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://visibleearth.nasa.gov/view.php?id=55580 |title=Nasa Visible Earth catalog 2001 |access-date=2015-05-13 |archive-date=2019-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190727140200/https://visibleearth.nasa.gov/view.php?id=55580 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 預報 ==
目前對太陽閃焰的預測仍然有其問題，因為沒有證據顯示太陽上的活躍區一定會發生閃焰，而且閃焰也不一定發生在活躍區。然而，太陽黑子和活躍區與閃焰有許多細直上的關聯。例如，磁場複雜的區域（基於視線的磁場），稱為會產生大閃焰的三角點。麥克因托倡建了簡單的黑子分類法，以外觀形狀的複雜性來分類黑子<ref>{{cite journal|last1= McAteer|first1= James|date= 2005|title= Statistics of Active Region Complexy|journal= The Astrophysical Journal|volume= 631|issue= 2|page= 638|publisher= IOP Publishing|url= http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005ApJ...631..628M|bibcode= 2005ApJ...631..628M|access-date= 2015-05-13|archive-date= 2019-04-01|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190401190555/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2005ApJ...631..628M|dead-url= no}}</ref>，通常被用做預測閃焰的一個起點<ref>{{cite journal |last1= Wheatland|first1= M. S.|date= 2008|title= A Bayesian approach to solar flare prediction|journal= The Astrophysical Journal|volume= 609|issue= 2|pages= 1134–1139|publisher= IOP Publishing|doi= 10.1086/421261|url= http://iopscience.iop.org/0004-637X/609/2/1134/pdf/0004-637X_609_2_1134.pdf|arxiv = astro-ph/0403613 |bibcode = 2004ApJ...609.1134W }}</ref>。預測通常用來顯示在24或48小時內發生M級或X極閃焰發生的概率，並由[[美國國家海洋暨大氣總署|NOAA]]處理這種的預測<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.swpc.noaa.gov/ |title=Space Weather Prediction Center |publisher=''NOAA'' |accessdate=August 1, 2012 |archive-date=2011-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110224183042/http://www.swpc.noaa.gov/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

